A '''modal property''' is a [[property]] representing possession of the qualities (especially action qualities) required to do something or get something done. It is a [[base concept]], one of the [[base concepts]] mentioned as [[base types]] in the [[WordNet]] [[ontology]] of [[semantics]]. It is not a [[mental property]]. It is not a [[physical property]].


